## `lua2dox_lua`

`lua2dox.lua` and `lua2dox_filter` is retrieved from `scripts/` in
<https://github.com/neovim/neovim.git>. Documentation of the very original version is available at
<http://tug.ctan.org/web/lua2dox/>.
